parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and jerking can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or lurch forward, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The transmission slips or jerks when shifting gears
often accompanied by a loud banging or grinding noise. The vehicle may hesitate or lurch forward when accelerating
and the engine RPM may surge or drop unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure to shift properly can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or lurch forward, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The transmission fails to shift properly
causing the vehicle to hesitate or lurch forward when accelerating. The vehicle may also experience sudden loss of power or stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The valve body failure can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to loss of power, stalling, or lurching forward, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The valve body failure can cause the transmission to slip or jerk when shifting gears
often accompanied by a loud banging or grinding noise. The vehicle may hesitate or lurch forward when accelerating
and the engine RPM may surge or drop unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the window regulator can cause the window to malfunction, leading to safety hazards such as water entry, poor visibility, and potential ejection of occupants. This can also lead to expensive repairs.
symptoms: The window will not roll up or down
makes a grinding noise
or falls down on its own. The window regulator may break
causing the window to become stuck or inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the rear window from the convertible top can cause water entry, poor visibility, and safety hazards. This can also lead to expensive repairs.
symptoms: The rear window detaches from the convertible top
creating an open space into the car
and fabric shrinks back from the glass.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating a potential failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag may deploy unexpectedly
or the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty airbag sensor can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating a potential failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag may deploy unexpectedly
or the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Issues with the seatbelt can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating a potential failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag may deploy unexpectedly
or the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadvertent airbag deployment can cause injury or distraction to the driver, increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag deploys unexpectedly
without any apparent reason or warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to deploy airbag in an accident can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag does not deploy in the event of an accident.
